    # vivi "It's something incredible to see the first time... But we don't have time to waste being amazed..."
    vivi "Es algo increíble verlo la primera vez... Pero no tenemos tiempo que perder en sorprendernos..."

# game/scripts/Events/Arabasta/Rainbase/ar_rainbase_h.rpy:234
